*There are two FCC IDs for the BEFW11S4 v2, FCC ID: :MXF-C901114 ([[Gemtek WL-375]], PRISM 2.5) and :MXF-C910308 ([[Gemtek WL-375P]], PRISM 3).
Some units list the FCC ID as just MXF-C901114 (see [http://www.squakmt.com/LinksysBEFW11S4.V2/ here]) while others list both (see [http://gallery.cdk.com/linksys?page=1 here]). :It is not known if the units which list both FCC IDs consist of a mix of both parts or are strictly the newer WL-375Ps. :It is also not known if there is a version listing strictly the newer FCC ID (v2.1?).
Specifications may be identical to the [[Linksys BEFW11S4 v2 (WL-375P)]].
